entry.title: Russia Tries to Tighten Grip on Occupied Areas of Ukraine
entry.content: As its military campaign to take more territory in the eastern Donbas region stalls, Moscow is trying to hold on to areas it occupies and Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky warns that fighting is set to intensify.
